---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy | Novel Signer"
	description="Privacy Policy for Novel Signer by CoderMana Technologies Private Limited."
>
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="mb-10">
			<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline">
				← Back to home
			</a>
		</div>

		<article class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200/70 dark:border-slate-800/70 bg-white/70 dark:bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
			<header class="mb-10">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-3">Legal</p>
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Effective date: April 7, 2026</p>
			</header>

			<div class="space-y-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-8">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
					<p>
						Novel Signer is provided by CoderMana Technologies Private Limited ("CoderMana," "we," "our," or "us"). This Privacy Policy explains how we handle personal information when you visit this website, contact us, download the Novel Signer desktop application, or use related support services.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Information we collect</h2>
					<p>We may collect the following categories of information:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li>Contact details you provide, such as your name, email address, company name, and the contents of your inquiry.</li>
						<li>Website usage information, such as pages visited, browser type, device information, approximate location derived from IP address, and referral information.</li>
						<li>Support and product feedback you send to us, including attachments, logs, screenshots, or descriptions of issues if you choose to provide them.</li>
						<li>Transactional or business information necessary to evaluate licensing, enterprise discussions, or customer support requests.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. How we use information</h2>
					<p>We use information we collect to:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li>Operate, maintain, and improve the website and Novel Signer-related services.</li>
						<li>Respond to questions, support requests, demos, onboarding requests, and enterprise discussions.</li>
						<li>Investigate bugs, security incidents, abuse, fraud, or misuse.</li>
						<li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce our agreements.</li>
						<li>Understand website traffic and product interest in aggregate.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Desktop files and signed content</h2>
					<p>
						Novel Signer is designed primarily as a desktop application. Documents, images, certificates, cryptographic credentials, and signatures you process in the app are intended to remain under your control on your systems unless you explicitly choose to share information with us for support. We do not claim ownership of your files, signed output, or signing credentials.
					</p>
					<p>
						If you send files, logs, or screenshots to us for troubleshooting, we will use them only for support, diagnostic, security, and service improvement purposes consistent with this Privacy Policy.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Legal bases</h2>
					<p>
						Where applicable, we process personal information based on legitimate interests, performance of a contract, compliance with legal obligations, and your consent where consent is required.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Sharing of information</h2>
					<p>We may share information:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li>With service providers who help us operate the website, communications, analytics, hosting, and support processes.</li>
						<li>With professional advisors, auditors, insurers, or legal authorities when reasonably necessary.</li>
						<li>In connection with a merger, financing, acquisition, reorganization, or sale of business assets.</li>
						<li>When required to comply with law, enforce our rights, or protect users, customers, or the public.</li>
					</ul>
					<p>We do not sell personal information for monetary consideration.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Data retention</h2>
					<p>
						We retain personal information for as long as reasonably necessary for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy, including support continuity, legal compliance, recordkeeping, dispute resolution, and enforcement of agreements.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">8. Security</h2>
					<p>
						We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards designed to protect personal information. No method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">9. Your rights</h2>
					<p>
						Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, restrict, object to, or export certain personal information. You may also have the right to withdraw consent where processing is based on consent. To make a request, contact us at <a href="mailto:namaste@codermana.com?subject=Novel%20Signer%20Privacy%20Request" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline">namaste@codermana.com</a>.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">10. International transfers</h2>
					<p>
						Your information may be processed in countries other than the one in which you reside. Where required, we take reasonable steps designed to ensure appropriate safeguards apply to such transfers.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">11. Children’s privacy</h2>
					<p>
						Novel Signer and this website are not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">12. Changes to this policy</h2>
					<p>
						We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">13. Contact us</h2>
					<p>
						For privacy questions, requests, or concerns, contact us at <a href="mailto:namaste@codermana.com?subject=Novel%20Signer%20Privacy%20Request" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline">namaste@codermana.com</a>.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</article>
	</main>
</Layout>
